1
00:00:09,039 --> 00:00:10,248
Hey there.How are you doing?
Hey there. 你好吗?

2
00:00:10,601 --> 00:00:12,418
Hi Pam.You know George,don't you?
Hi Pam. 你认识George, 对吗?

3
00:00:12,821 --> 00:00:13,240
Sure.Hi.
当然. 你好.

4
00:00:13,703 --> 00:00:14,348
Where are you going?
你去哪里呀?

5
00:00:14,638 --> 00:00:16,223
Jarmusch gave me the afternoon off.
Jarmusch下午给我放假.

6
00:00:16,916 --> 00:00:19,216
We were working until 2a.m.last night.
昨晚我们一直工作到凌晨两点.

7
00:00:19,787 --> 00:00:20,860
You weren't cooking,were you?
你们不是在烧菜吧?

8
00:00:21,374 --> 00:00:22,901
No.We were finishing the new menu.
No. 我们在拟定新菜单.

9
00:00:23,232 --> 00:00:26,480
Jarmusch has changed everything.Now it's classic cuisine.
Jarmusch把什么都改变了. 现在是经典菜品.

10
00:00:27,244 --> 00:00:28,485
We've been planning it for weeks.
我们已经为此准备了好几个星期了.

11
00:00:29,231 --> 00:00:30,417
It sounds like a lot of work.
听起来很大的工作量.

12
00:00:31,305 --> 00:00:31,914
It's been endless.
真是没完没了.

13
00:00:32,528 --> 00:00:34,221
And Jarmusch has been driving me crazy.
Jarmusch要把我逼疯了.

14
00:00:35,198 --> 00:00:36,073
Jarmusch is crazy.
Jarmusch真是疯了.

15
00:00:37,151 --> 00:00:38,892
Do you have to show the new menu to anyone?
你们必须把新菜单给饭店的其他人看吗?

16
00:00:39,527 --> 00:00:39,858
Oh yeah.
Oh yeah.

17
00:00:40,277 --> 00:00:42,608
Jarmusch was showing it to Simon and Nino when they left.
Jarmusch正在给Simon和Nino看呢,在我离开的时候.

18
00:00:43,026 --> 00:00:44,060
Sharon asked for it,too.
Sharon也要求要看.

19
00:00:44,501 --> 00:00:46,121
Everyone has their two cents to put in.
每个人都想发表自己的见解.

20
00:00:46,607 --> 00:00:48,955
So,who was cooking while you were planning?
那么, 你们在拟菜单的时候谁在做饭呢?

21
00:00:49,399 --> 00:00:49,764
Another cook!
另一个厨师!

22
00:00:51,468 --> 00:00:52,777
We were just going to lunch.
我们正准备去吃午餐.

23
00:00:54,284 --> 00:00:55,032
Would you like to join us?
你愿意和我们一块儿去吗?

24
00:00:55,564 --> 00:00:59,266
Thanks,but the last thing I want to do is look at a menu.
谢谢, 我现在最不愿意的事情就是看菜单了.

